com.mumfrey.liteloader.interfaces

Interface Loadable<L>

  • Type Parameters:
    L - base class type for Comparable so that implementors can specify their Comparable type.
    All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<L>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    LoadableMod<L>, MixinContainer<L>, TweakContainer<L>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LoadableFile, LoadableMod.EmptyModContainer, LoadableModClassPath, LoadableModFile

    public interface Loadable<L>
extends java.lang.Comparable<L>
    Interface for things which are loadable, essentially mods and tweaks
    Author:
    Adam Mummery-Smith
